B. Media Outreach 

Billboards:  Ketchum  rolled  out  highway  billboards  on  outdoor  advertising  space 
in  five  additional  markets  in  August,  and  has  now  made  agreements  for  donated 
space in a total of 55 markets. The new billboards went up in Duluth, MN; Spring-
field, MO; Yuma (El Centro), AZ; Kansas City, MO; and Dayton, OH. 

