Is  Under  Way,  but  Preparedness  to  Manage  an  Increase  in  Subsidy  Demand  Is  Unclear,  GAO– 
08–1040 (Washington, D.C.: September 16, 2008). 

2 Eligible converter boxes range in price from $40 to over $90. 

