are covering various parts of the constituencies. 

Senator DORGAN. Let me just give you a North Dakota example. 
In North Dakota, 52,900 coupons have been requested, 21,000 have 
been  used,  and  13,000  have  expired.  Almost  14,000  have  expired. 
What is going to happen with the expired coupons, and why do you 
think  so  few  of  the  many  coupons,  52,000  requested,  21,000  re-
deemed? Why so few redeemed and what is going to happen to the 
