Ms. BAKER. We are actually pleased with the redemption rate of 
coupons.  Many  coupon  programs  you  see  are  in  the  single-digit  re-
demption  rate.  So  we  are  pleased  with  the  redemption  rates  and 
they  do  seem  to  be  creeping  up,  which  we  also  think  is  important. 
I  have  actually  sat  out  at  our  call  center,  and  when  people  call 
for  coupons,  they  typically  order  two.  We  might  have  thought  that 
they  might  have  ordered  one,  but  they  typically  order  two.  And  it 
is  more  about  ‘‘how  many  can  I  have’’,  as  opposed  to  ‘‘how  many 
do I need?’’ So I think that may attribute to why we are seeing two 
being ordered instead of just one. 

Senator  DORGAN.  I  would  encourage  you  to  do  some  review  of 
