expired will not be renewed. Is that correct? 

Ms.  BAKER.  They  will  not  be  reissued,  but  importantly,  the 
money for those coupons is put back into the pot of money that will 
be  recycled  and  more  coupons  will  be  sent  out  from  those  coupons 
that are not redeemed. 

Senator  DORGAN.  Mr.  Goldstein,  if  you  are  among  those  of  us 
who  are  worried  about  coming  up  to  a  date  and  just  turning  the 
switch—they did not do that in England, as I said, and I have read 
some  about  what  the  experience  was  in  England.  If  you  are  one  of 
