Mr. MARTIN. One of the benefits of doing the test in Wilmington 
was to identify exactly where that digital cliff is and the impact of 
where  viewers  used  to  be  able  to  get  a  signal  and  then  were  no 
longer able to. 

I  think  that  there  are  two  different  issues  that  occurred  in  Wil-

mington that people should be aware of. 

I  should  just  say,  Senator,  for  the  record  I  am  nervous  about 
what  is  going  to  occur  in  February  as  well.  We  are  doing  all  that 

