Ms.  BAKER.  I  think  the  entire  DTV  coalition  agrees  that  the 
problems that we see in this area need an awful lot more consumer 
education. So certainly we will be working with our partners. 

Again,  I  think  the  most  important  from  our  perspective  is  to  get 
