mize  that.  Many  of  the  calls  that  we  received  were  not  that  they 
were not aware of it. As I indicated, we have received actually only 
about 100 calls during the whole time since September 8 from con-
sumers who said they were unaware of the early transition. 

But  there  were  problems  and  challenges  for  viewers  both  in 
